* If you want to install gatsby through your local gitbash. First of all install Node.js from https://nodejs.org/en.
* Now open gitbash in your locall and check the below commands
# node -v
# npm -v
# npm install -g gatsby-cli
# gatsby new static-website
# cd static-website
# gatsby develop
# http://localhost:8000/ --> A new website will appear.
# gatsby build
# cd public/